sequenceDiagram
    participant PF as Prefect (news_flow)
    participant TASK as pipeline_task
    participant PIPE as run_pipeline (etl/pipeline.py)
    participant EXT as run_extraction (etl/extract.py)
    participant SCR as scrapers (Kapitalis, RSS)
    participant TRF as transform_articles (etl/transform.py)
    participant LOAD as save_articles (etl/load.py)
    participant DB as PostgreSQL (articles)

    PF->>TASK: pipeline_task(max_pages)
    activate TASK
    TASK->>PIPE: run_pipeline(max_pages)
    activate PIPE
    PIPE->>EXT: run_extraction(max_pages)
    activate EXT
    EXT->>SCR: scrape()
    SCR-->>EXT: list[Article]
    deactivate EXT
    EXT-->>PIPE: articles

    PIPE->>TRF: transform_articles(articles)
    activate TRF
    Note right of TRF: embeddings (e5-small)<br/>sentiment (cardiffnlp)<br/>theme + region (LLM)
    TRF-->>PIPE: transformed dicts
    deactivate TRF

    PIPE->>LOAD: save_articles(transformed)
    activate LOAD
    LOAD->>DB: INSERT ... ON CONFLICT (url) DO UPDATE
    DB-->>LOAD: rowcount
    deactivate LOAD
    LOAD-->>PIPE: saved

    PIPE->>DB: record_pipeline_metrics(...)
    PIPE-->>TASK: {extracted, transformed, loaded}
    deactivate PIPE
    TASK-->>PF: result
    deactivate TASK
    Note over PF,TASK: retries=2, retry_delay_seconds=60 on failure
